data.description: Click the Virtual Tour link to view the 3D walkthrough. Charming single story home just minutes from Hwy 44 and I-25 providing easy access to retail, restaurants, and entertainment. Within a mile to Light Rail and right around the corner from multiple walking trails and Liberty Hills Park! Step inside to find vaulted ceilings and a spacious living room with a cozy fireplace to enjoy during the colder months. The kitchen has beautiful wooden cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, and a sunny dining area. The primary bedroom features walk-out access to the deck and a massive walk-in closet proving plenty of storage space. The basement is finished and has additional living space and 2 bedrooms creating a wonderful space to enjoy with guests if needed. The backyard has a sunny deck and is fenced in providing additional privacy. No HOA. New Furnace. New electrical panel & circuits. Swamp cooler works great.  Recent upgrades include: all new carpet and fresh interior paint on the main level. Welcome home!
